annotations: Sausalito

Sausalito (Spanish for “small willow grove”) is a city located just to the north of San Francisco across the Golden Gate Bridge. Sausalito’s climate can be surprisingly cool due to the proximity of San Francisco Bay. It is known for its houseboat communities.
